Interface VirtualServer

All Superinterfaces:
Remote
All Known Subinterfaces:
VirtualServerRmi, VirtualServerSocket
All Known Implementing Classes:
RmiServer, SocketServerHandler
public interface VirtualServer extends Remote
Interface defining the server methods that must be made accessible to clients to allow interaction with the server's game logic (controller). All methods throw Exception to handle potential communication or logic issues.
